  "body": "I am trying to reply [this transaction](https://etherscan.io/tx/0x8544e64257d79e6725d053117baec4c23ea968211c89cc6b78b3e1b1a7e27c04), which was reverted on the main chain due to being out of gas.\r\n\r\nBut Hardhat reported `Transaction reverted without a reason string` instead of `out of gas`.\r\n\r\nI am doing it with the right hard fork `muirGlacier`.\r\n\r\n**Reproduction steps**\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nconst BLOCK = 12038871;\r\n\r\nawait hre.network.provider.request({\r\n  method: \"hardhat_reset\",\r\n  params: [{ forking: { jsonRpcUrl: PROVIDER } }],\r\n});\r\nconst block = await ethers.provider.getBlockWithTransactions(BLOCK);\r\nconst txs = block.transactions;\r\nconst txs_raw = block.transactions.map(getRawTransaction);\r\n\r\nawait hre.network.provider.request({\r\n  method: \"hardhat_reset\",\r\n  params: [{\r\n    forking: { jsonRpcUrl: PROVIDER, blockNumber: BLOCK - 1 }\r\n  }],\r\n});\r\nlet tx_raw = txs_raw[73];\r\nlet tx_mock = await ethers.provider.sendTransaction(tx_raw); // error\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ ts-node --files scripts/main.ts\r\nError: Transaction reverted without a reason string\r\n    at <UnrecognizedContract>.<unknown> (0x2647bd8777e0c66819d74ab3479372ea690912c3)\r\n    at <UnrecognizedContract>.<unknown> (0x3c06b757e24815f2dcd71baa9516bca2d691f8fc)\r\n    at async HardhatNode._mineBlockWithPendingTxs (/home/dan/git/tmp/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/node.ts:1582:23)\r\n    at async HardhatNode.mineBlock (/home/dan/git/tmp/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/node.ts:435:16)\r\n    at async EthModule._sendTransactionAndReturnHash (/home/dan/git/tmp/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/modules/eth.ts:1494:18)\r\n    at async HardhatNetworkProvider.request (/home/dan/git/tmp/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/provider.ts:108:18)\r\n    at async EthersProviderWrapper.send (/home/dan/git/tmp/node_modules/@nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers/src/internal/ethers-provider-wrapper.ts:13:20)\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 1.\r\n```\r\n",
